Package: surfspec
Title: PAE tools for imaging spectroscopy
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Alexandre", "Castagna", email = "alexandre.castagna@ugent.be", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Dorian", "Bas", email = "dorian.bas@uantwerpen.be", role = "ctb"))
Description: This package provide functions for imaging spectroscopy tailored 
    for the needs of the Protistology and Aquatic Ecology (PAE) research group at 
    Ghent University, Belgium. Those needs are: in air hemispherical-directional
    reflectance of macrophytes and sediments cores.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.3.0),
    sp (>= 1.3.0),
    raster (>= 2.6.0),
    rgdal (>= 1.3.0)
Imports:
    magrittr (>= 1.5)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
